Bread is the sustenance of everything inside of the Breaking Point app

What is Bread?

Bread is BP's social currency which allows you to build up your profile, unlock new features, win trophies on game and season leaderboards, and earn badges.

How can I earn Bread?

  • Adding a custom profile avatar, banner, and team flair
    +50 for each for a total of +150 Bread

  • Live Game Viewership Bread
    +10 Bread for each match page that you go into while the game is live.

  • Pre-game polls (+10 per match)
    Before a game starts you can go into a match page and pick which team you think will win. You can win 10 Bread per game won. You earn +10 more bread for each streak of 5 that youre on (e.g. you will earn 20 Bread if youre on a 5-10 correct prediction streak, 30 Bread if youre on a 11-15 correct prediction streak, 40 on an 16-20 streak, etc).

  • Post-game MVP polls (+10 per match)
    After a game finishes, for 30 minutes, you can go into a match page and pick the match MVP. Each time you vote for a match MVP, you earn +10 Bread

  • Commenting (once a day)
    +10 Bread for leaving a comment once a day

  • Reacting to a match or article (once a day)
    +10 Bread for reacting to a match or article once a day

  • Player & Team Cards
    Your player and team cards generate bread each time they play this season, with rewards scaling based on their performance.

We are improving and adding more ways to earn Bread.
